401
00:30:48,673 --> 00:31:01,139
ARKAN

402
00:31:01,840 --> 00:31:04,473
Dans le calme du soir

403
00:31:04,540 --> 00:31:06,673
聞こえるよ サラ…

404
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:12,440
